structure.unit: TITLE TO PROPERTY AND RESTRICTIONS ON USE, OWNERSHIP, AND ALIENATION

law.history: Repealed 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 118, sec. 19, effective June 17, 1978. -- Created 1972 Ky. Acts ch. 284, sec. 1.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Care of cemeteries and burial grounds -- Legislative bodies of counties and cities may prescribe requirements.
